video.title: Discovery Market Eco Crew
video.description: Our Eco Crew characters recently made their debut at the Discovery Science Center in Orange County, CA! Artifact’s team of character designers and animators brought these Virtual Clerks to life with spunk and smarts to educate kids (of all ages) about making environmentally friendly choices.

video.title: Ford Fund 2011
video.description: A spot for the Ford Motor Company's Ford Fund initiative, highlighting the group's dedication to helping fund education efforts in Nashville, TN and around the country.

video.title: MWB - Cadence Bank / Benjamins
video.description: Who knew ol' Ben was so savvy with an iPhone? This was a fun one - creating an illustrated dollar-themed piece for MWB and their client Cadence Bank.

video.title: TBS - Team Coco Tablet App
video.description: Conan O'Brien's team at TBS turned to Artifact to premier his new Team Coco App, bringing some retro-futuristic fun to all the glorious benefits of the application's features for your tablet or smart phone. Turner's Sponsor Shop gave us yet another excuse to have way too much fun at work.

video.title: Cartoon Network - Star Wars Clone Wars Microsite
video.description: A project that involves Star Wars Clone Wars AND super cool toys? Count us in! Our TV and Micro-Site designs for this Cartoon Network project feature stylized posters, creatively connecting the Blasters and the SWCW brands.

video.title: Fernbank Natural History Museum Digital Book
video.description: This digital book, created to replace a laminated binder, illustrates the habitat around Gray's Coral Reef off the coast of Georgia. The exhibit has mounted controls outside of the screen.

video.title: Luckie Brand Animation
video.description: Luckie & Co. asked Artifact to bring their agency’s history to life through light-hearted design and animation based on original illustrations by Eleonora Marton. A great synopsis of one of our favorite agencies.

video.title: TBS - Hop Movie Promo
video.description: Our LA and Atlanta teams worked together with our friends at Turner's Sponsor Shop to create these very drummy... bunny... funny spots for tbs. Shooting Russell Brand and playing with bunnies and chicks all day... it's a tough life, huh?

video.title: Cartoon Network - Carnival
video.description: Cotton candy, anyone? Join the stars of Cartoon Network as we move through an enticing and mysterious Carnival world, created by Artifact's team of designers, art directors, and animators.

video.title: Ramey Agency - Entergy Carbon
video.description: Our friends at Ramey asked us to create this friendly Webisode for Entergy's website as a part of the company's Earth Day 2010 campaign.

video.title: TNT and TBS - Tron Movie Promo
video.description: Charged with integrating the ultra-tech style of TRON Legacy with clips of TBS and TNT's most popular shows, we created a light cycle to tear through the transitions between brand promotions.

video.title: Discovery Science Center Montage
video.description: Artifact Design created the on-screen elements for several new interactive exhibits at Discovery Science Center in Orange County, CA. Game themes included grocery store shopping, garbage sorting, and hazardous home items. We designed and animated characters, instructions and interactive touch screens for all phases of the project.
